  <div class='commenttext-admin'>
  <p>Jean-Francois,
<br />Both are set exactly the same way:
<br />* Make sure you have the color scheme file in your ~/.vim/colors folder  
<br />* Then create or modify your ~/.vim/vimrc file (startup settings go here)
<br />* Add these lines to it:
<br />   set background=dark 
<br />   colorscheme ir_black
<br />   syntax on</p>

<p>Also, I'd upgrade vim if possible (I use MacPorts in OS X to do that), as 7.1.x is the current version.</p>
</div>   
