<p>          Colors      Bright Colors
<br />Black     #4E4E4E     #7C7C7C
<br />Red       #FF6C60     #FFB6B0
<br />Green     #A8FF60     #CEFFAB
<br />Yellow    #FFFFB6     #FFFFCB
<br />Blue      #96CBFE     #FFFFCB
<br />Magenta   #FF73FD     #FF9CFE
<br />Cyan      #C6C5FE     #DFDFFE
<br />White     #EEEEEE     #FFFFFF
</p>
