          <li class="alt"><a name="comment_150"> </a>
  <div class="commentname">
      hone
    <span class="commentmeta">December 21, 2008 16:03&nbsp;</span>
  </div>

  <div class='commenttext'>
  <p>to get the popup to display correctly in xterm, you have to override the cterm settings next to PmenuSel.  This is what I changed mine to:</p>

<p>  hi Pmenu          guifg=#f6f3e8     guibg=#444444     gui=NONE      ctermfg=white       ctermbg=darkgray    cterm=NONE
<br />  hi PmenuSel       guifg=#000000     guibg=#cae682     gui=NONE      ctermfg=black       ctermbg=lightgreen  cterm=NONE
</p>
