  <p>I added the following three lines to the if vim 7 section after hi search, it adds matching coloring to vim tabs:</p>

<p>hi TabLineSel     guifg=green       guibg=darkgray  gui=NONE      ctermfg=green       ctermbg=darkgray    cterm=NONE
<br />hi TabLineFill    guifg=darkgray    guibg=NONE      gui=NONE      ctermfg=darkgray    ctermbg=NONE        cterm=underline
<br />hi TabLine        guifg=darkgray    guibg=NONE      gui=NONE      ctermfg=darkgray    ctermbg=NONE        cterm=underline</p>

<p>you might consider adding this or not :-)</p>
